            <div corresp="#c4393f2">
                <head>Aden, Arabia</head>
                <p>James L. Park, V. C. took over the office from Consul Davis June 16, 1924.</p>
                <p>James L. Park, V.C., took over charge from V. C. Aldridge, Apr. 1, 1978, turned
                    over office to V. C. Huston, July 21, 1928.</p>
                <p>As of June 1947 Department discontinued usage of Aden, Aden - henceforth referred
                    to as Aden only.</p>
                <p>(Aden is a territory under the British Crown - same category as Hong Kong and
                    Singapore) information obtained from PB - Miss Bullick 1-25-50 (bec)</p>
